Description_lang: Fire a shot that poisons your target, causing them to take $?s389882[${$m1*(1+($389882m1/100))}][$s1] Nature damage instantly and an additional $?s389882[${$o2*(1+($389882m1/100))}][$o2] Nature damage over $d.$?s378014[Serpent Sting's damage applies Latent Poison to the target, stacking up to $378015u times. $@spelldesc393949 consumes all stacks of Latent Poison, dealing $378016s1 Nature damage to the target per stack consumed.][]

description_blz.en_US: Fire a shot that poisons your target, causing them to take 159 Nature damage instantly and an additional 725 Nature damage over 18 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Realiza un disparo que envenena a tu objetivo, le inflige 159 p. de daño de naturaleza de forma instantánea y 725 p. más de daño de naturaleza durante 18 s.
description_blz.pt_BR: Dispara um projétil que envenena o alvo, fazendo-o receber 159 de dano de Natureza instantaneamente, mais um adicional de 725 de dano de Natureza ao longo de 18 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Feuert einen Schuss ab, der Euer Ziel vergiftet und ihm so sofort 159 Naturschaden sowie zusätzlich 725 Naturschaden im Verlauf von 18 Sek. zufügt.
description_blz.en_GB: Fire a shot that poisons your target, causing them to take 159 Nature damage instantly and an additional 725 Nature damage over 18 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Realiza un disparo que envenena al objetivo, que recibe 159 p. de daño de Naturaleza al instante y 725 p. de daño de Naturaleza más durante 18 s.
description_blz.fr_FR: Vous tirez un coup qui empoisonne votre cible et lui inflige 159 points de dégâts de nature instantanément, puis 725 en 18 s.
description_blz.it_IT: Spara un colpo che avvelena il bersaglio, infliggendo 159 danni da natura istantaneamente e 725 danni da natura aggiuntivi in 18 s.
description_blz.ru_RU: Выстрел отравляет цель, нанося ей 159 ед. урона от сил природы мгновенно и еще 725 ед. урона от сил природы за 18 сек.
description_blz.ko_KR: 적을 중독시키는 투사체를 발사해 즉시 159의 자연 피해를 입히고, 추가로 18초에 걸쳐 725의 자연 피해를 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 射擊目標使其中毒，對方立刻受到159點自然傷害，並在18秒內額外受到725點自然傷害。
description_blz.zh_CN: 射击目标，使目标中毒，立即受到159点自然伤害，并在之后的18秒内承受总计725点自然伤害。
